Humans are worse than dogs!” 🐾🔥 TV actors strongly oppose the Supreme Court’s recent verdict ordering all stray dogs in Delhi–NCR to be shifted to shelters. With nearly 10 lakh strays and limited infrastructure, they call it a “death warrant” 💔 and urge compassion, vaccination drives, and better facilities instead of punishment. Candle marches and NGOs across India prove one thing—animals deserve homes, not blame. ✨🐶
